did.abstract: Collection of medium format mounted black and white and color reproductions of French painting. Content varies from original photographic prints to reproductions from magazines and other published sources. Some sections have accompanying clippings folders.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: The materials are open for research.

userestrict.head: Conditions Governing Use
userestrict.p: Copyright has not been transferred to Yale University. Further use of this material may be subject to the copyright laws of the United States (Title 17, United States Code) or to site license or other rights management terms or conditions.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: French Painting Photograph Collection, Arts Library, Yale University

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Collection of medium format mounted black and white and color reproductions of French painting. Content varies from original photographic prints to reproductions from magazines and other published sources. Some sections have accompanying clippings folders.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: Arranged alphabetically by artist. Individual artist material is further subdivided by location of the work. The individual artist portion is preceded by a grouping arranged chronologically and then by location.
